\c 7
\nb
\v 1 UElisha wasesithi: Zwanini ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*; itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Ngalesisikhathi kusasa \w iseya\w** lempuphu ecolekileyo \add lizathengiswa\add* \w ngeshekeli\w**, lamaseya amabili \w ebhali\w** ngeshekeli, esangweni leSamariya\x + 7.18.\x*.
\v 2 Induna inkosi eyayeyeme esandleni sayo\x + 7.17,19. 9.25. 15.25.\x* yasiphendula umuntu kaNkulunkulu, yathi: Khangela, \add uba\add* iN\nd kosi\nd* ibingenza amawindi emazulwini, kungenzeka linto yini? Wasesithi: Khangela, uzakubona ngamehlo akho, kodwa kawuyikudla okwakho\x + Mal. 3.10. Gen. 7.11.\x*.
\p
\v 3 Njalo kwakulamadoda amane ayengamalephero ekungeneni kwesango\x + Levi 13.46.\x*, athi omunye komunye: Sihlaleleni lapha size sife?
\v 4 Uba sisithi: Sizangena emzini, lendlala isemzini, sizafela khona. Njalo uba sihlala lapha, sizakufa futhi. Ngakho-ke, wozani, si\add ye\add*wela enkambeni yamaSiriya; uba esiyekela siphile, sizaphila; uba-ke esibulala, sizakufa nje.
\v 5 Asesukuma kusahwalala ukuya enkambeni yamaSiriya; esefike ekucineni kwenkamba yamaSiriya, khangela-ke, kwakungelamuntu khona.
\v 6 Ngoba iNkosi yenza ibutho lamaSiriya lizwe umsindo wezinqola, umsindo wamabhiza, umsindo webutho elikhulu; athi omunye komunye: Khangela, inkosi yakoIsrayeli isisiqhatshele amakhosi amaHethi lamakhosi amaGibhithe ukuzamelana lathi.
\v 7 Asesukuma abaleka kusahwalala, atshiya amathente awo lamabhiza awo labobabhemi bawo, inkamba njengoba injalo, abaleka ngenxa yempilo yawo.
\v 8 Amalephero la esefike ekucineni kwenkamba, angena kwelinye ithente, adla anatha, athatha lapho isiliva legolide lezigqoko, ayakufihla; abuyela angena kwelinye ithente, athatha lapho, ayakufihla.
\v 9 Asesithi omunye komunye: Kasenzi kuhle. Lolusuku lusuku lwemibiko emihle, kodwa sizithulele thina. Uba silinda kuze kube yikukhanya kwekuseni, isijeziso sizasifica. Khathesi-ke, wozani siyebikela indlu yenkosi.
\v 10 Asesiza, amemeza kumlindi wesango womuzi, abatshela esithi: Sifike enkambeni yamaSiriya, khangela-ke, bekungelamuntu khona kumbe ilizwi lomuntu, kodwa amabhiza ebotshelwe labobabhemi bebotshelwe, lamathente enjengoba enjalo\x + 7.10. Joha. 4.6.\x*.
\v 11 Wasebiza abalindi bamasango, basebebikela indlu yenkosi phakathi.
\p
\v 12 Inkosi yasivuka ebusuku, yathi encekwini zayo: Sengizalitshela ukuthi amaSiriya enzeni kithi. Ayazi ukuthi silambile, ngakho aphumile enkambeni uku\add ya\add*catsha egangeni esithi: Nxa bephuma emzini, sizababamba bephila, besesingena emzini.
\v 13 Enye yenceku zayo yasiphendula yathi: Ake bathathe amahlanu emabhizeni aseleyo, aseleyo phakathi ko\add muzi\add*, (khangela, afanana lexuku lonke lakoIsrayeli elitshiywe kuwo, khangela, afanana lexuku lonke lakoIsrayeli eliqothuliweyo), kasithume, sibone.
\v 14 Basebethatha amabhiza amabili enqola; inkosi yasithuma emva kwebutho lamaSiriya isithi: Hambani, libone.
\v 15 Basebewalandela kwaze kwaba seJordani; khangela-ke, indlela yonke yayigcwele izembatho lempahla amaSiriya ayekulahlile ekuphangiseni kwawo. Izithunywa zasezibuyela, zayibikela inkosi.
\v 16 Abantu basebephuma bayiphanga inkamba yamaSiriya. Ngakho iseya lempuphu ecolekileyo \add laselithengiswa\add* ngeshekeli, lamaseya amabili ebhali ngeshekeli, njengokwelizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*\x + 7.1.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Inkosi yasibeka induna eyayeyeme esandleni sayo \add ukuba ngumlindi\add* phezu kwesango. Abantu bayinyathela esangweni yaze yafa\x + 7.2.\x*, njengokutsho komuntu kaNkulunkulu owakhuluma ekufikeni kwenkosi kuye\x + 6.32.\x*.
\v 18 Kwasekusithi njengokutsho komuntu kaNkulunkulu enkosini esithi: Amaseya amabili ebhali ngeshekeli, leseya lempuphu ecolekileyo ngeshekeli phose ngalesisikhathi kusasa azakuba sesangweni leSamariya\x + 7.1\x*.
\v 19 Induna yasimphendula umuntu kaNkulunkulu yathi: Khangela-ke, \add uba\add* iN\nd kosi\nd* ibingenza amawindi emazulwini, kungenzeka linto yini? Kodwa wathi: Khangela, uzakubona ngamehlo akho, kodwa kawuyikudla okwakho.
\v 20 Kwaba njalo-ke kuye, ngoba abantu bamnyathela esangweni waze wafa\x + 7.2.\x*.